### Create a book (admin) -> 200
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Authorization: Basic admin admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer",
  "author": "Andrew Hunt",
  "genre": "Software",
  "publicationYear": 1999
}


### Create a second book (admin) -> 200
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Authorization: Basic admin admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "genre": "Software",
  "publicationYear": 2008
}


### Get all books (user) -> 200
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books
Authorization: Basic user user


### Get book by id (user) -> 200
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Authorization: Basic user user


### Get a book by non existant id (user) -> 404
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/999999
Authorization: Basic user user

### Delete a book by non existant id (admin) -> 404
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/99999
Authorization: Basic admin admin

### Update a book by non existant id (admin) -> 404
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/99999
Authorization: Basic admin admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer (2nd Ed.)",
  "author": "Andrew Hunt",
  "genre": "Software",
  "publicationYear": 2019,
  "available": false
}


### Update a book (admin) -> 200
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Authorization: Basic admin admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer (2nd Ed.)",
  "author": "Andrew Hunt",
  "genre": "Software",
  "publicationYear": 2019,
  "available": false
}


### Find books by author (user) -> 200
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/author/Andrew%20Hunt
Authorization: Basic user user


### Find available books (user) -> 200
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/available
Authorization: Basic user user


### Delete a book by id (admin) -> 204
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/2
Authorization: Basic admin admin


### Blank title — should fail validation (admin) -> 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Authorization: Basic admin admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "   ",
  "author": "Andrew Hunt",
  "genre": "Software",
  "publicationYear": 1999
}


### Future publication year — should fail validation (admin) -> 400
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Authorization: Basic admin admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Time Machine",
  "author": "H.G. Wells",
  "genre": "SciFi",
  "publicationYear": 3000,
  "available": true
}


### No credentials GET -> 401 Unauthorized
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

### No credentials GET by ID-> 401 Unauthorized
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1

### No credentials DELETE -> 401 Unauthorized
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/1

### No credentials PUT -> 401 Unauthorized
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer (2nd Ed.)",
  "author": "Andrew Hunt",
  "genre": "Software",
  "publicationYear": 2019,
  "available": false
}

### Bad password -> 401 Unauthorized
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books
Authorization: Basic admin wrongpassword


### User tries to create a book -> 403 Forbidden
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Authorization: Basic user user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Should Be Forbidden",
  "author": "Nobody",
  "genre": "Software",
  "publicationYear": 2020
}


### User tries to update a book -> 403 Forbidden
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Authorization: Basic user user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Should Be Forbidden",
  "author": "Nobody",
  "genre": "Software",
  "publicationYear": 2020,
  "available": true
}


### User tries to delete a book -> 403 Forbidden
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Authorization: Basic user user
